{"tid":964420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"秦皇掃六合【新年滅門】不滿遭妻子家人忽視 泰男開槍殺6人包括親生子女","createTime":"2019-01-01T09:59:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-01T17:51:29.000Z","uid":65346,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7cf1d1cfbdd9df67082b41273cf3bc6face04391","tid":964420,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T09:59:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190101/59092809\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190101%2F59092809&d=gU8nps7zQsY9NRt2s4Sj8G6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=defb2f09\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190101%2F59092809&h=11380ee2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190101/59092809</a><br />\n<br />\n真係六國大封相 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">泰國</span>南部春蓬府（Chumphon）一名男子本來與妻子家人一起開除夕派對，怎料剛踏入2019年僅10分鐘，男子疑因不滿自己被妻子家人冷落，竟然開槍大開殺戒，連殺6人包括自己兩名年僅9歲及6歲的子女，兇手殺人後吞槍自殺。<br />\n事發於當地一間美容院，當時素普（Sucheep Sornsung）正與妻子家人舉行除夕派對，怎料卻釀成滅門慘案。警方周二表示，素普當時喝得爛醉，然後拔出手槍放在桌上。「全部受害人都是兇手的家人，包括他的9歲兒子和6歲女兒。6名受害人分別頭部或身體中槍&hellip;&hellip;兇手不滿自己身為女婿，卻不受妻子家人歡迎。」<br />\n除了兩名孩子外，其餘4名死者分別是2男2女，年齡介乎47歲至71歲。"},{"pid":"6f80b7cdbc1325c1cf26ae53fb05162ad465f1ed","tid":964420,"uid":168698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T10:13:34.000Z","msg":"人地個女個老公呀，醫生黎架你話呀幾巴弊呀<br />\n<br />\nby仆街親戚"